<emphasis bold="true" box="[279,448,2287,2326]" pageId="0" pageNumber="133">Material:</emphasis>
Holotype ♂, paratype 
<emphasis box="[859,893,2288,2326]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="133">♂</emphasis>
, Switzerland, Ticino, Valle Mesolcina, Fiume Moesa at Buffalora Falls, 12 Aug. 2001, R Zwick. Specimens in 
<emphasis box="[1048,1124,2333,2371]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="133">15%</emphasis>
